    "en": {
      "title": "The pilots fell asleep and missed the flight",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that two pilots of an Ethiopian passenger plane fell asleep and missed the airport.",
        "This 'Boeing 737' aircraft has arrived from Khartoum, Sudan to Addis Ababa, Ethiopia. The plane was flown by the autopilot system, and the pilots had left the flight operations to the autopilot system and slept.",
        "Missing the airport and the runway, the pilots were woken up by air traffic control officials who kept calling them."
      ],
